    {
      "id": "PopularPost188933",
      "post_content": "@nevenshinko  \nNo, it can't because Replicate puts copies right on the stack. The controller (your opponent in your example) isn't 'playing' them, which is the key word on this card. The same with Storm and other abilities that specifically say 'copy'.   \n  \nSomething like Cascade, however, does trigger this card because Cascade allows the player to 'cast' the exiled card. In Magic, the words 'cast' and 'play' are interchangeable in this situation.",
      "posted_by": "OmegaSerris",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost188933\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">@nevenshinko<br/>No, it can't because Replicate puts copies right on the stack. The controller (your opponent in your example) isn't 'playing' them, which is the key word on this card. The same with Storm and other abilities that specifically say 'copy'. <br/><br/>Something like Cascade, however, does trigger this card because Cascade allows the player to 'cast' the exiled card. In Magic, the words 'cast' and 'play' are interchangeable in this situation.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '188933'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy50832\">OmegaSerris</span>\r\n                                (8/17/2011 11:39:53 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.p